&lt;li&gt;Coordinate and prepare executives for internal and external meetings, board sessions, investor calls, and speaking engagements.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Draft, review, and manage high-stakes correspondence on behalf of leadership.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Anticipate executive needs and act with autonomy to keep priorities on track.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
